INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

1. Unpack toplist<ver>.tar.gz file
2. Change variables in config.php
3. Upload files onto server
4. Change 'banners', 'style', 'backup' directory & 'cheat.log' file permission to 777
5. Change 'images/logo.jpg' & 'images/button.jpg' with your graphics
6. Point your browser to http://yourdomain.com/toplist_directory/install.php
7. And that's all. :)


Administration panel: http://www.yourdomain.com/toplist_directory/admin.php